yle=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Trượt v&aacute;n trượt </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black; height:24.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:155.8pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Go skiing </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:24.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:156.05pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">/ˈskiɪŋ/ </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:24.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:155.8pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Trượt tuyết </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black; height:24.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:155.8pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Listen to CDs </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:24.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:156.05pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:24.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:155.8pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-