&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:32.5pt; width:293.3pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:10px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Một panh (= 0.57 l&iacute;t ở Mỹ) (dung t&iacute;ch)&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"height:23.9pt; vertical-align:bottom; width:18.0pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&bull;</span> </span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:23.9pt; vertical-align:bottom; width:172.85pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">To stay in sb&#39;s favour:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:23.9pt; vertical-align:bottom; width:293.3pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:10px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Vẫn được l&ograve;ng ai, vẫn được ai ủng hộ/b&ecirc;nh vực&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&bull;</span></span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Senior (adj) (vai vế):&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ở cấp cao hơn, ở cấp tr&ecirc;n </span>&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n', 7, 0, '2018-12-24 15:55:08', '2018-12-24 15:55:08', 4, '', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `posts` (`idtin`, `title`, `content`, `user_id`, `is_public`, `createdate`, `updatedate`, `idnhom`, `anhtrichdan`, `videotrichdan`, `noidungtrichdan`) VALUES
(116, 'VIII. PASSAGE 8 ', '<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">From the moment we returned from the violent heat of East Africa we were soaked by the </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">continuous drizzle of a fine English summer It was not a particularly promising introduction to life back in England after three years of being baked under the Kenyan sun. Nevertheless the leaden skies of August could not make me any less enthusiastic about my fast approaching return to British education. I was about to I enter a South London comprehensive.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">At the time I was totally unaware of the shock that was awaiting me one much worse than adapting to the dismal climate. I was just looking. I forward to making lots of new friends and getting stuck into school life. I was under the impression that the other pupils would be interested in my stories about Africa and would instantly warm to my sparkling personality. Unfortunately, however, I had really been looking at thing! through rose-tinted glasses and it wasn‟t long before I experienced a much darker, unappealing side of things.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">On the first day of term I bounded into the noisy assembly hall eager to size up my new classmates. As I scanned the room, which was packed with huddled clusters of teenagers, I got my first suspicions that becoming part of their cosy groupings might not be as easy as I had imagined. They all seemed to have an air of belonging as they laughed and chatted together. I tried to look relaxed and carefree but no one so much as glanced in my direction, let alone tried to introduce themselves. It turned out to be an uncomfortable morning in my new class, but as the hours dragged by, I tried to work out what would be a good plan of attack for getting in on the action.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">It began to dawn on me that what was needed was a little effort on my part. So at break, I swallowed my pride and strolled over to a group of boys standing by the gates to say hello. The tallest was a dark-haired lad with a permanent sneer on his face. &ldquo;Where did you get your shiny shoes, mate?&rdquo; was all he said. I looked down at my new leather shoes and noticed that everyone else was wearing the latest trainers. Before I could think of something amusing to say, they had begun to wander back to class leaving me red-faced and dumbfounded by the gate.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">At the end of my first day, I stormed out of the classroom as soon as the final bell rang, almost knocking over a girl who was passing along the corridor. I was fuming. I had arrived that morning full of hopes for a bright new future, only to have them dashed on the hard ocks of teenage indifference. The dark clouds above my head seemed to settle around me as I trudged back home, reminding me of how grim the day had been, I was so enraged that I almost didn‟t hear someone calling my name and I turned round to see a boy from my class, Brian, running to catch up with me.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&ldquo;You haven‟t exactly been made to feel welcome today, have you?&rdquo; he said beaming at me. &ldquo;You could say that,&rdquo; I replied sarcastically. He laughed and suggested I give him my mobile number and he would text me later. &ldquo;But I haven‟t got a mobile!&rdquo; I told him, my heart sinking once again. A look of utter amazement spread across his face and he sud&not;denly went very quiet while I waited for him to reply. Finally, he took a deep breath. &ldquo;Look, if I were you, I‟d get a mobile. Everyone has one! </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:41px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">And while you‟re at it, sort yourself out with a decent pair of trainers.&rdquo; Then he was gone.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I walked into the house and flung my blazer and bag down in the hall. My mum popped her head round the living room door and asked how my first day had gone. &ldquo;Can you please tell me why I need a mobile phone and trainers if I want to make any friends?&rdquo; I replied. I was so stony-faced that I think she knew better than to reply, so she just stood there looking confused as I stomped up the stairs and slammed my bedroom door shut.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">How did the writer feel about being back in England?&nbsp; </span></em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">A.</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">He was pleased to be back in a cooler climate.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">He was unsure of his feelings.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">He was optimistic, despite the bad weather.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">He was nervous about starting school.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The phrase &ldquo;looking at things through rose-tinted glasses&rdquo; (paragraph 2) means...... </span></em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">A.</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Only seeing a situation from your own point of view. </span></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Seeing things in a very simple way.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Only seeing the pleasant aspects of something.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Having too much confidence in yourself.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">When the writer first met his classmates, he&hellip;..&nbsp; </span></em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">A.</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Felt a little afraid of them.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Suspected he had little in common with them.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Realised it might take some time before they accepted him.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Found he lacked the confidence to introduce himself. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">When the writer approached the group of boys, they responded by......&nbsp; </span></em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">A.</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Making fun of him.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Making a joke&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ignoring him.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Complimenting him.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The writer uses the phrase &ldquo;I stormed out of the classroom&rdquo; (paragraph 5) to show that he left a room&nbsp; </span></em></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Quickly and noisily because he was angry.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">As soon as he could.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Without anyone seeing him leave.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Without looking where he was going </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"6\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">On the way home, a boy from the writer&rsquo;s class&nbsp; </span></em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">A.</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Offered him an apology.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Gave him some advice.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lost his temper with him. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Criticised his attitude.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">When the writer spoke to his mother, he&nbsp; </span></em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">A.</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Quickly regretted it.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Wished he had said it in a different way.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Felt annoyed by her response.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Understood why she didn&rsquo;t reply.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"8\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">How did the writer‟s attitude change during the passage?&nbsp; </span></em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">A.</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">He began to lose confidence in himself.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">He began to see things as they really were.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">He began to realise the need to change.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">He began to understand himself better. - to be soaked bị ướt sũng&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">GLOSSARY 8 </span></span></strong></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"TableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; margin-left:64px; width:497.1pt\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"height:23.9pt; vertical-align:top; width:18.0pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&bull;</span> </span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"he