</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C &ndash; C &ndash; B &ndash; A &ndash; A &ndash; B &ndash; D &ndash; A&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">A &ndash; D &ndash; C &ndash; B &ndash; C &ndash; D &ndash; A&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">D &ndash; A &ndash; A &ndash; D &ndash; C &ndash; A&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', 7, 0, '2018-12-24 15:59:07', '2018-12-24 15:59:07', 4, '', NULL, NULL),
(120, 'I. 5 BƯỚC LUYỆN VIẾT TIẾNG ANH ', '<h2 style=\"margin-left:64px; margin-right:2px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1.</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Xác định mục ti&ecirc;u b&agrave;i viết </span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">D&ugrave; viết với h&igrave;nh thức n&agrave;o cũng đều c&oacute; mục đ&iacute;ch, bạn cần x&aacute;c nhận lại mục ti&ecirc;u của m&igrave;nh khi viết b&agrave;i n&agrave;y l&agrave; g&igrave;. Điều n&agrave;y l&agrave; để bạn dễ d&agrave;ng t&igrave;m hiểu nội dung li&ecirc;n quan l&agrave;m tư liệu cho b&agrave;i viết. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">H&atilde;y nhớ lại: </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:113px; margin-right:345px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">o</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">L&yacute; do bạn viết đoạn văn n&agrave;y </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">o</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bạn sẽ tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y về điều g&igrave; </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">o</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mục ti&ecirc;u truyền đạt đến người đọc l&agrave; g&igrave; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:64px; margin-right:2px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2.</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Gạch đ&acirc;̀u dòng l&ecirc;n khung b&agrave;i viết </span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đừng vội v&agrave;ng lao v&agrave;o viết ngay khi nhận được y&ecirc;u cầu. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nếu l&agrave; đoạn văn ngẫu hứng, bạn c&oacute; thể tự do theo &yacute; m&igrave;nh cho thống nhất c&aacute;c c&acirc;u. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nếu l&agrave; b&agrave;i viết đầy đủ, khung mẫu rất quan trọng. Cũng như viết một b&agrave;i viết tiếng Việt, trước khi viết b&agrave;i th&igrave; phần d&agrave;n &yacute; hết sức quan trọng. Điều n&agrave;y gi&uacute;p qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh viết b&agrave;i kh&ocirc;ng bị lan man, lạc đề sang những vấn đề kh&aacute;c. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Khi liệt k&ecirc; khung b&agrave;i viết, bạn n&ecirc;n ch&uacute; &yacute; để ch&uacute;ng được sắp xếp theo thứ tự, c&oacute; li&ecirc;n quan với nhau cho đ&uacute;ng định hướng. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Một b&agrave;i viết cơ bản thường c&oacute; 3 phần: </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:113px; margin-right:204px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">o</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mở b&agrave;i: giới thiệu, dẫn nhập chủ đề </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">o</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Th&acirc;n b&agrave;i: Củng cố cho luận để ch&iacute;nh, gồm từ 2 &ndash; 3 đoạn văn </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">o</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Kết luận: nhắc lại luận đề v&agrave; tổng kết </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:64px; margin-right:2px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3.</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Xác định cấu trúc ngữ pháp sẽ dùng </span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Cấu tr&uacute;c ngữ ph&aacute;p v&agrave; cấu tr&uacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin l&agrave; khung xương của b&agrave;i viết. Dựa tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c gạch dầu d&ograve;ng vừa n&ecirc;u trong khung b&agrave;i viết để x&aacute;c định lại cấu tr&uacute;c xuy&ecirc;n suốt trong b&agrave;i. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mỗi một chủ đề được n&ecirc;u n&ecirc;n c&oacute; những cấu tr&uacute;c tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;i kh&aacute;c nhau. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Chẳng hạn khi viết một đoạn truyện ngắn, bạn kh&ocirc;ng thể d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;ch so s&aacute;nh t&iacute;nh chất, ưu nhược điểm của vấn đề. Cấu tr&uacute;c n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c n&agrave;y l&agrave; d&ograve;ng thời gian kết lại những g&igrave; đ&atilde; xảy ra. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:64px; margin-right:2px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4.</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Viết thẳng vấn đề </span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">L&agrave; người mới học luyện viết, bạn h&atilde;y thẳng thắn v&agrave;o vấn đề đưa ra, đừng d&agrave;i d&ograve;ng hoa l&aacute; c&agrave;nh tr&aacute;nh gặp nhiều lỗi hơn v&agrave; g&acirc;y kh&oacute; chịu cho người đọc. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Viết đơn giản l&agrave; c&aacute;ch viết rõ r&agrave;ng, s&aacute;ng &yacute; v&agrave; dễ hiểu nhất. Bạn n&ecirc;n luyện c&aacute;ch viết n&agrave;y ngay từ khi mới bắt đầu, dạng như xuất hiện &yacute; tưởng n&agrave;o th&igrave; viết ngay &yacute; tưởng ấy sau đ&oacute; sắp xếp lại cho hợp l&yacute;. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bước 5: Xem lại v&agrave; chia sẻ </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; bước ho&agrave;n thiện cuối c&ugrave;ng của luyện viết. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">H&atilde;y xem lại to&agrave;n bộ nội dung m&igrave;nh đ&atilde; viết xem ch&uacute;ng c&oacute; vấn đề g&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng, c&oacute; nhầm lẫn hay sai s&oacute;t ở đ&acirc;u. V&agrave; cuối c&ugrave;ng l&agrave; chia sẻ cho bạn b&egrave; c&ugrave;ng biết những trải nghiệm bạn vừa tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y! </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 7, 0, '2018-12-24 16:00:24', '2018-12-24 16:00:24', 1, '', NULL, NULL),
(121, 'II. VIẾT THƯ: ', '<p style=\"margin-left:64px; margin-right:2px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1.</span></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Cấu tr&uacute;c chung của bức thư bằng tiếng Anh: </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">a)</span></span></em><em> </em><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Heading: </span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Heading hay c&ograve;n gọi l&agrave; ti&ecirc;u đề. Phần n&agrave;y sẽ l&agrave; t&ecirc;n của bức thư m&agrave; bạn muốn gửi. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">b)</span></span></em><em> </em><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Inside address: </span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Địa chỉ b&ecirc;n trong (Th&ocirc;ng thường chỉ d&ugrave;ng trong thư c&ocirc;ng việc m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng sử dụng trong thư th&acirc;n mật.) </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">o</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Th&ocirc;ng tin người viết: Địa chỉ, điện thoại, fax hay địa chỉ h&ograve;m thư (e-mail) được đặt đầu thư, ở ch&iacute;nh giữa hoặc b&ecirc;n phải bức thư.Tr&aacute;nh d&ugrave;ng t&ecirc;n ri&ecirc;ng của bạn trừ khi đ&acirc;y l&agrave; thư từ c&aacute; nh&acirc;n v&igrave; khi viết thư giao dịch, người viết thường d&ugrave;ng t&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng ty. </span></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ng&agrave;y th&aacute;ng: Trong tiếng Anh bạn n&ecirc;n ch&uacute; &yacute; khi viết ng&agrave;y th&aacute;ng. Người Anh sẽ viết ng&agrave;y trước th&aacute;ng sau (04/ 02/ 2000) c&ograve;n người Mỹ lại viết th&aacute;ng trước ng&agrave;y sau (02/ 04/ </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:137px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2000). Để tr&aacute;nh hiểu nhầm bạn n&ecirc;n viết đầy đủ thứ ng&agrave;y th&aacute;ng năm như: 4 February 2000 hoặc February 2nd, 2000). C&aacute;ch viết n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng chỉ tr&aacute;nh nhầm lẫn m&agrave; c&ograve;n lich sự hơn c&aacute;ch chỉ d&ugrave;ng số. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:none\">\r\n	<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">T&ecirc;n v&agrave; địa chỉ người nhận: C&aacute;ch tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y t&ecirc;n, chức danh, t&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng ty, v&agrave; địa chỉ giao dịch của đối t&aacute;c (người nhận) giống như c&aacute;ch bạn tr&igrave;nh bầy t&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng ty của bạn v&agrave; c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin li&ecirc;n quan ở đầu thư. Chỉ c&oacute; một điểm kh&aacute;c l&agrave; những th&ocirc;ng tin về người nhận được đặt ở b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i thư hay v&igrave; b&ecirc;n phải hay ch&iacute;nh giữa. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&aacute;ch xưng h&ocirc; đầu thư.</span> </span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">V&iacute; dụ: Dear Mr. Smith; Dear Mrs. Smith; Dear Miss Smith; Dear Ms. Smith; Dear Sir/Madam/ Sirs/Gentlemen&hellip; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">c)</span></span></em><em> </em><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Body </span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Phần th&acirc;n của bức thư được tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y th&agrave;nh khối với những đoạn văn mạch lạc, r&otilde; r&agrave;ng tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y th&ocirc;ng tin m&agrave; bạn muốn chuyển tới người đọc. Đầu d&ograve;ng sẽ bắt đầu từ lề tr&aacute;i, kh&ocirc;ng thụt v&agrave;o như c&aacute;ch viết thư trước đ&acirc;y. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">d)</span></span></em><em> </em><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Complimentary close </span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Phần cuối thư nếu giao tiếp với những người bạn kh&ocirc;ng quen, người Anh thường d&ugrave;ng những cụm như: Yours sincerely, Yours faithfully, Yours truly. Hoặc với người bạn th&acirc;n quen: Your loving friend, Love, Your loving student, Lovely&hellip; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">K&egrave;m th&ecirc;m chữ k&yacute; v&agrave; họ t&ecirc;n đầy đủ của người viết. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Trong trường hợp c&oacute; t&agrave;i liệu gửi k&egrave;m theo thư, bạn c&oacute; thể viết cuối thư ghi ch&uacute; về số lượng t&agrave;i liệu gửi k&egrave;m.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">V&iacute; dụ: Enc: 2.. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:65px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2.</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Một số lưu &yacute; khi viết thư bằng tiếng Anh </span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Kh&ocirc;ng viết tắt: Phải viết đầy đủ I am, I will, I have seen, I do not,&hellip; kh&ocirc;ng được viết I&rsquo;am, I&rsquo;ll, I don&rsquo;t, I&rsquo;ve seen. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Kh&ocirc;ng sử dụng từ th&ocirc;ng tục, tiếng l&oacute;ng, c&aacute;c từ th&acirc;n mật v&iacute; dụ như: wanna, kid, dad, mate&hellip;trừ c&aacute;c bức thư đ&atilde; qu&aacute; th&acirc;n mật. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">H&atilde;y lễ độ d&ugrave; cho đang bực tức: d&ugrave;ng Dear ở đầu thư, v&agrave; d&ugrave;ng please khi muốn y&ecirc;u cầu. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">H&atilde;y viết cho ngắn gọn, nhưng đủ &yacute;. C&acirc;u văn cũng vậy, ngắn, kh&ocirc;ng d&ugrave;ng c&acirc;u phức với 3, 4 mệnh đề (complex sentense). C&acirc;u phải c&oacute; đầy đủ subject, verb, direct object v&agrave; indirect object nếu c&oacute;. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">H&atilde;y nhớ d&ugrave;ng v&agrave; d&ugrave;ng ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c c&aacute;c dấu chấm c&acirc;u: chấm, chấm phẩy, phẩy, dấu hai chấm. nếu 1 &yacute; ch&iacute;nh c&oacute; nhiều &yacute; phụ, d&ugrave;ng dấu gạch đầu d&ograve;ng. Hạn chế d&ugrave;ng hoặc tuyệt đối kh&ocirc;ng d&ugrave;ng dấu chấm than (!). </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Cuối thư: Regards, Best Regards, Hai c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y d&ugrave;ng th&ocirc;ng dụng trong nhiều t&igrave;nh huống. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Sincerely yours, d&ugrave;ng trong thư xin việc, thư khiếu nại, thư mời v&igrave; mang nghĩa &ldquo;ch&acirc;n th&agrave;nh&rdquo;. Faithfully yours, d&ugrave;ng trong thư trả lời của nh&agrave; cung cấp cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, v&igrave; mang nghĩa &ldquo;trung th&agrave;nh&rdquo;. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:64px; margin-right:2px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3.</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Những bức thư tiếng Anh mẫu kinh điển </span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Một bức thư chia buồn được xếp v&agrave;o h&agrave;ng kinh điển đ&oacute; l&agrave; bức thư nổi tiếng Abraham Lincoln viết cho b&agrave; Bixby, mẹ của năm người con trai đ&atilde; hy sinh về tổ quốc. </span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:41px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Washington, November 21, 1864. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dear Madam, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I have been shown in the files of the War Department a statement of the Adjutant-General of Massachusetts that you are the mother of five sons who have died gloriously on the field of battle. I feel how weak and fruitless must be any words of mine which should attempt to beguile you from the grief of a loss so overwhelming. But I cannot refrain from tendering to you the consolation that may be found in the thanks of the Republic they died to save. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I pray that our Heavenly Father may assuage the anguish of your bereavement, and leave you only the cherished memory of the loved and lost, and the solemn pride that must be yours to have laid so costly a sacrifice upon the altar of freedom. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Yours very sincerely and respectfully, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Abraham Lincoln. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:88px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Reply to a friend on his interest in the English </span></span></em></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">5, Market Street </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ipoh </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">15th May, 19... </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dear Ali, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:5px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thank you for your delightful letter which came a short while ago. I am pleased to learn of the new interest you feel in the English language, for it is the first step in your journey to success. No one, in his right senses, can deny that proficiency in English is essential to personal progress and happiness today. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">One of the ways of improving your English is to read books on a variety of subjects. If you read books on one or two subjects only, your vocabulary will not expand fast enough. As you might know the English vocabulary consists of more than 600,000 words. Each subject has its own vocabulary. Therefore, the more subjects you read in English and more words you will learn to express yourself with greater ease and satisfaction. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">You should also learn the basic rules of grammar. It is indeed difficult to write English confidently without some knowledge of grammar. The simplest books on English Grammar are those written by Milon Nandy. They can be found in any book shop. I am sure you have seen many of them. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Please write to me again if you need any help. Though I am not a master of the English language, yet I think I can be of some help to you. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Yours sincerely, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Marvin </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:88px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Letter of thanks to a teacher </span></span></em></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lake View School, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">7, Main Road </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Penang </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">15th August, 2004 </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dear Miss Jane, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">As you are aware, I did very well in my last examination. I now wish to thank you for all the good work that you had done for me and for all the others in the class. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">You must believe me when I say that we found your lessons very interesting, and your kind words were an added inspiration to us to study hard. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I am sure it was only because of your good work that I and many others in the class did so well in the examination. I shall always remember you with affection, gratitude and respect as well my friends who passed the examination together with me. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">You are indeed a teacher of outstanding calibre and it is a unique privilege to be taught by you. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Yours loving student, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ruby Nandy </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:88px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Declining an invitation to a wedding </span></span></em></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">15, Jalan Multan, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Muar, Johor, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">6th April, 19... </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dear Swee Moi, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thank you for asking me to attend your sister&#39;s wedding on the 10th of this month. Your sister is indeed very lucky, and I am sure that the wedding will be an event to remember. I would certainly like to attend such a wedding, but as you know, my mother is still very ill and I have to be near by to attend to her needs. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:23px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">You must therefore excuse me from attending the party. I shall try to meet your lovely sister and the new member of your family, your brother-in-law, as soon as I am able to do so. Your loving friend, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Kamanah </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:88px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">e)</span></span></em><em> </em><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I know you often sports at weekends, what&#39;s your favorite sport? Tell me about it. </span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dear Linh, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Thanks for your letter. I&#39;m glad to know that you and your family are always healthy and happy. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:41px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Now I feel healthier and more comfortable, too. I think that is the result of doing exercise frequently. These days, I usually jog around the park near my house every afternoon. Most of time, I work in the office. It will be not good to sit a fixed place. Thus I determined to do exercise more frequently to keep the body healthy and the sport which choose is jogging. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I enjoy jogging a lot because jogging helps me to be fitter and more enduring. I think jogging gives us a lot of benefits not only for body but for mind. It is the most efficient way of achieving fitness through exercise and burns more calories because it is a high impact exercise. Jogging is also very good for your heart, improves the muscle tone and strength, and relieves stress, beside also deal with heart disease. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I usually spend 2 hours to jog every afternoon with my friends. We often make appointment each other at Thong Nhat Park to do exercise together. It is much happier than doing alone. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1px; margin-right:144px; text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">And you, what is your favorite sports? Can you share you thinking about it? </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lovely, </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mai </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', 7, 0, '2018-12-24 16:01:13', '2018-12-24 16:01:13', 1, '', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `posts` (`idtin`, `title`, `content`, `user_id`, `is_public`, `createdate`, `updatedate`, `idnhom`, `anhtrichdan`, `videotrichdan`, `noidungtrichdan`) VALUES
(122, 'I. NHỮNG ĐIỂM CẦN LƯU Ý KHI NÓI TIẾNG ANH ', '<h2 style=\"margin-left:64px; margin-right:2px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1.</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">T&igrave;m hiểu về từ v&agrave; nghĩa của cụm từ </span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nhiều sinh vi&ecirc;n học từ vựng v&agrave; cố gắng kết hợp nhiều từ với nhau để tạo th&agrave;nh một c&acirc;u c&oacute; nghĩa. T&ocirc;i rất kinh ngạc khi c&oacute; nhiều từ sinh vi&ecirc;n của t&ocirc;i biết, nhưng ch&uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng tạo th&agrave;nh một c&acirc;u c&oacute; nghĩa được. Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n l&agrave; do họ kh&ocirc;ng học Cụm Từ. Khi trẻ con học ng&ocirc;n ngữ, ch&uacute;ng học cả từ v&agrave; Cụm từ với nhau. Cũng vậy, bạn cần phải t&igrave;m hiểu v&agrave; học c&aacute;c cụm từ. Nếu bạn biết 1000 từ, bạn sẽ c&oacute; khả năng n&oacute;i 1 c&acirc;u đ&uacute;ng. Nhưng nếu bạn biết 1 Cụm từ, bạn c&oacute; thể l&agrave;m đ&uacute;ng h&agrave;ng trăm c&acirc;u. Nếu bạn biết 100 Cụm Từ, bạn sẽ rất ngạc nhi&ecirc;n khi biết c&oacute; bao nhi&ecirc;u c&acirc;u đ&uacute;ng m&agrave; bạn c&oacute; thể n&oacute;i. Cuối c&ugrave;ng, khi bạn biết chỉ 1000 Cụm từ th&ocirc;i, bạn sẽ gần như l&agrave; một người n&oacute;i Tiếng Anh bản địa. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:88px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:64px; margin-right:2px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2.</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Luyện tập lại những g&igrave; bạn n&oacute;i </span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Đọc, Nghe v&agrave; N&oacute;i gần như l&agrave; những kh&iacute;a cạnh quan trong nhất của tất cả c&aacute;c ng&ocirc;n ngữ. Điều đ&oacute; cũng đ&uacute;ng với Tiếng Anh. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, chỉ c&oacute; N&oacute;i l&agrave; y&ecirc;u cầu để th&agrave;nh thạo Tiếng Anh. Điều đ&oacute; rất b&igrave;nh thường khi trẻ nhỏ học n&oacute;i trước, trở n&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh thạo sau đ&oacute; mới bắt đầu đọc v&agrave; viết. V&igrave; vậy thứ tự tự nhi&ecirc;n l&agrave; nghe, n&oacute;i, đọc rồi mới viết. Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n nhiều người c&oacute; thể đọc v&agrave; nghe bởi v&igrave; họ đều luyện tập. Nhưng để n&oacute;i Tiếng Anh th&ocirc;ng thạo th&igrave; bạn cần phải luyện tập n&oacute;i kia. Đừng dừng lại ở phần nghe, v&agrave; khi bạn học, bạn kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n chỉ nghe. H&atilde;y n&oacute;i to l&ecirc;n t&agrave;i liệu m&agrave; bạn đang nghe v&agrave; luyện tập những g&igrave; bạn nghe. luyện tập n&oacute;i thật to cho tới khi miệng của bạn v&agrave; n&atilde;o của bạn c&oacute; thể n&oacute;i chung m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng tốn sức. Bằng c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m việc đ&oacute;, bạn sẽ c&oacute; khả năng n&oacute;i Tiếng Anh một c&aacute;ch lưu lo&aacute;t.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:88px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:64px; margin-right:2px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3.</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tiếng Anh mọi l&uacute;c mọi nơi&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&oacute; khả năng n&oacute;i một ng&ocirc;n ngữ kh&ocirc;ng li&ecirc;n quan g&igrave; tới việc bạn th&ocirc;ng minh bao nhi&ecirc;u. Mọi người đều c&oacute; thể học n&oacute;i bất cứ ng&ocirc;n ngữ n&agrave;o. Điều n&agrave;y đ&atilde; được chứng minh bởi mọi người tr&ecirc;n thế giới. Ai cũng c&oacute; thể n&oacute;i được &iacute;t nhất 1 ng&ocirc;n ngữ. D&ugrave; bạn th&ocirc;ng minh hay thiếu một &iacute;t chất x&aacute;m, bạn vẫn c&oacute; khả năng n&oacute;i được 1 ng&ocirc;n ngữ. Điều n&agrave;y c&oacute; thể l&agrave;m được bằng c&aacute;ch luyện ng&ocirc;n ngữ v&agrave;o mọi l&uacute;c. ở nước bạn, bạn nghe v&agrave; n&oacute;i ng&ocirc;n ngữ của bạn ngay lập tức. Bạn sẽ ch&uacute; &yacute; thấy rằng nhiều người n&oacute;i Tiếng Anh giỏi l&agrave; những người đ&atilde; học ở một trường luyện n&oacute;i Tiếng Anh. Họ c&oacute; thể n&oacute;i Tiếng Anh kh&ocirc;ng phải v&igrave; họ đến một trường dạy n&oacute;i Tiếng Anh, m&agrave; v&igrave; họ c&oacute; một m&ocirc;i trường m&agrave; ở đ&oacute; Tiếng Anh l&uacute;c n&agrave;o cũng được sử dụng bởi những người xung quanh. Cũng c&oacute; nhiều người đi du học v&agrave; học được rất &iacute;t, bởi v&igrave; l&uacute;c họ đến trường dạy n&oacute;i Tiếng Anh, nhưng họ chỉ gặp được bạn b&egrave; từ đất nước của họ v&agrave; họ kh&ocirc;ng luyện tập Tiếng Anh. Bạn kh&ocirc;ng cần phải đi đ&acirc;u d&oacute; để trở th&agrave;nh một người n&oacute;i Tiếng Anh giỏi. Bạn chỉ cần l&agrave;m cho bạn bị bao phủ bởi Tiếng Anh. Bạn c&oacute; thể l&agrave;m được điều n&agrave;y bằng c&aacute;ch thỏa thuận với bạn b&egrave; của bạn, rằng bạn sẽ chỉ n&oacute;i Tiếng Anh. Bạn cũng c&oacute; thể mang theo một chiếc iPod v&agrave; nghe c&aacute;c c&acirc;u Tiếng Anh ngay lập tức. như bạn thấy đấy, bạn c&oacute; thể đạt được th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng bằng c&aacute;ch thay đổi m&ocirc;i trường xung quanh bạn. &quot;Tiếng Anh h&oacute;a&quot; bạn v&agrave; bạn sẽ học được nhanh hơn gấp nhiều lần. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:88px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:64px; margin-right:2px\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">4.</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Luyện n&oacute;i </span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dưới đ&acirc;y l&agrave; 15 chủ đề để tham khảo v&agrave; luyện tập tại nh&agrave; &ndash; khuyến kh&iacute;ch bạn đọc tại nh&agrave;, đọc thật to, rõ r&agrave;ng, sai cũng kh&ocirc;ng sao, h&atilde;y tập thật nhiều, tập c&ugrave;ng với bạn b&egrave; để c&ugrave;ng sửa lỗi v&agrave; c&oacute; thể y&ecirc;u cầu gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n nghe bạn đọc để sửa lỗi. V&agrave; khi đ&atilde; đủ tự tin, h&atilde;y bu&ocirc;ng s&aacute;ch xuống v&agrave; tự m&igrave;nh n&oacute;i.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:88px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">a)</span></span></em><em> </em><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The means of transport you like most. </span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">If I have to decide which mean of transport I like most, it&#39;ll be a car. Nowadays it is really necessary for me and my family. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Firstly, it is safer to drive a car than to ride a motorbike because in a car there are air bags, seat belts, car alarm, etc, that prevent us from being injured if you have an accident. Driving a car at night on a lonely road will safer than riding a motorbike. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Secondly, you never have to think about the weather (such a rain, sun, storm, and dark at night) when you drive. A car has air-conditioner which helps you to avoid getting wet, dust... so it help to keep you healthy. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In the third place, a car is comfortable and fast. You can pretty much travel wherever you want whenever you want within your local area, without having to worry about the departure times and delays of the public transport system. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Furthermore, you will feel comfortable and relaxed with the CD and DVD machines on the car. You can listen to music and you can have pleasure of driving. When you are tired, you can stop the journey and rest. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Finally, if you have just the one car between you and your family, it can be possible to share the vehicle between all of the family members thus providing everyone with a mode of transport at all times. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">b)</span></span></em><em> </em><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The most useful machine in the twentieth century. </span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Among the most useful inventions in the last century, I find the computer the most important because of these reasons: </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">First, when the computer is connected to the Internet, it is a good way of learning and getting information. You can read newspapers on line and download lots of information from the web pages. Besides, you can learn online as well. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Second, computers is convenient because it helps you work faster by typing, printing document and storing data if you want. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Finally, computer is a good way to entertain with many kinds of games and entertainments. There are a lot of games and on line activities like forum or Facebook for you to share ideas and information with your friends. You can also listen to music or watch movies if you like. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In short, computers are really useful and important to my life and my work. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Your favorite leisure activity (for women). </span></span></em></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I often cook when I have free time because cooking is a joyful and relaxing activity for me. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">First, cooking a good meal brings happiness to my family. All the members in my family can gather around the table and enjoy the food I cook and talk and share the joy with each others. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Second, cooking is my favorite hobby because I&#39;m a woman. Cooking is one way to show my feminine character and to show my responsibility in the family. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Finally, cooking helps me reduce stress of everyday hard work and makes me relaxed. When I cook, I can forget the problems that I have and just pay attention to the cooking. Maybe, after relaxing, I feel much happier and I can solve my problem. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In conclusion, cooking is my favorite activity when I have free time. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The advantages of living in the countryside. </span></span></em></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Living in the countryside is really good for your life because of these reasons: </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">First, living in the country can bring you a clean environment. The air is fresher and there are lots </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:41px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">of trees, rice fields and rivers, you can walk on the fields or along the rivers to enjoy the clean and fresh air there in the early morning. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Second, living in the countryside is cheaper than in the city because people there have lower income and don&#39;t have the habit of spending a lot of money. If you live in the country, you can save a lot of money. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Finally, people in the country are more friendly and opener than people in the city because they </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:41px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">live near each other. People live together in a small village so they can talk countryside can have festivals and you can join and fell very happy. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In conclusion, there are many benefits of living in the country. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">e)</span></span></em><em> </em><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The disadvantages of living in the city. </span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Many people find it difficult and unpleasant to live in the city because of these reasons: </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">First, the air in the city is getting more and polluted because the traffic is so heavy, the city roads are in bad conditions and the population is really big. There are fewer and fewer trees, lakes and rivers. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Second, the cost of living is much higher than in the rural areas. People have to spend more money on food, drink, clothes and other activities like traveling and entertainment, while the salary has not been much improved. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Finally, life in the city is more dangerous than in the countryside because of night clubs, discotheques, casinos... City people are easily attracted by social evils such as drinking, drug or gambling, etc. So, there are more crimes because some people don&#39;t want to work but only want money to play. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In short, living in the city has many disadvantages so people have to struggle a lot to survive. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">f)</span></span></em><em> </em><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Talk about your weekend activities. </span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Weekend time is my favorite time in the week because I can enjoy myself and do many relaxing </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:41px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">activities I like. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In the morning, after a relaxing breakfast, I often call some of my friends to ask them to go shopping with me. We spend the whole morning going shopping and then have lunch in a restaurant in the center of Hanoi. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1px; text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Then, I come back home for a nap. In the afternoon, I often go swimming with my neighbor if </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">the weather is hot. In winter I go jogging in the central park instead. I usually have dinner with my family during weekend, so we can talk with each other and share our stories. After dinner, I sometime listen to music or surf the net to chat with friends or check emails. I usually do not go to bed late because I will have lots of work on Monday. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In short, living in the city has many disadvantages so people have to struggle a lot to survive. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"7\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Talk about on of your hobbies. </span></span></em></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">People may have different hobbies such as listening to music, watching T.V, dancing. playing games or collecting things. My hobby is to read books. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:none\">\r\n	<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">enjoy reading many types of books, but my favorite is detective. I like reading stories about Sherlock Holmes of author Conan Doyle. I often read books in the evening after I finish preparing things for the next day&#39;s work. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">When I have free time, I often go to bookstores to look for new books. Once a week, I go to the city library to read there. I sometimes read books on line if I cannot get hard copies of the books I want. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Books help me relax a lot after days of hard work. Thanks to books, I can broaden my knowledge and learn new things. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"8\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The most interesting place you have been to. </span></span></em></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">have been to many places in Vietnam, but the most interesting place that I always remember is Da Nang, the beautiful coastal city in Vietnam. It&#39;s wonderful to me because of these reasons: </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">First, the scenery in Da Nang is ideal for us to go sunbathing. We can swim in the blue and clear sea water or do sunbathing on the soft sand beach under the yellow and warm sunshine. The air is so fresh and pure. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1px; text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Second, the local sea food are fresh, delicious but not expensive. For example, tourists can enjoy </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:41px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">different kinds of seafood such as crab, prawn, lobster, seashell, etc. Also, the people there are friendly, sociable and polite. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Third, there are many interesting activities to do beside playing football, tennis on the beach, building sandcastles on the beach or watching the sunrise. For example, we can sail on a board trip to the Cu Lao Cham and watch the mountain scenery on the way. Also, we may visit Ba Na Hill. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">For these reasons, Da Nang has always been one of my favorite tourist attractions. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-roman\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The importance of learning foreign languages. </span></span></em></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Nowadays, it is very important to learn a foreign language because of these reasons: </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">First, learning a foreign language, English for example, helps us learn and get information about new things in the world. There are a lot of books written in English, French, Chinese, etc. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Second, it help us feel confident when we travel abroad. We can talk very easily with people in other countries and learn a lot from them. We can use the language to work and do business without an interpreter. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Finally, though a foreign language we learn we can learn more about the people of that country, we know a lot about their culture and society and customs and traditions. We can become friends of many people so our life is more interesting. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In short, when we know a foreign language we can open a new to our world. Because of the benefits of learning foreign languages, one should know at least one foreign language. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:64px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">j)</span></span></em><em> </em><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ways to have a good health. </span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">If you want to have good health, you should follow these pieces of advice: </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">First, you should eat healthy food: lots of fruits, vegetable, fish and drink enough water everyday to stay healthy. The Japanese eat a lot of fish so they live very long. You should eat less meat and fat food because they may cause heart diseases and increase the cholesterol level in your blood. Fruits and vegetables no only bring you lots of vitamins and minerals but also help you have a better immune system. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Second, you should exercise everyday by choosing a suitable sport such as jogging, tennis, swimming, yoga, etc. They not only make you strong but help you relax as well. So, it helps you keep fit and stay healthy. If you don&#39;t have much time, you just need to do morning exercises regularly. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Finally, you need to have regular health check &ndash; up. If you have some problems with your health, you should go to the doctor immediately before it gets more serious. You should visit the doctor regularly in order to find out any diseases you may have, so that you have a better chance to get rid of it. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:89px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In short, if you take this advice, you will have a good health. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"11\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Talk about your favorite television program. </span></span></em></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Among many programs and channels available on TV these days such as the current news programs, sport programs, entertaining programs, educational programs and movie programs, etc, I like the program &quot;the World of Animals&quot; most. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">This program is usually shown on VTV2 everyday at 8.30 in the evening. It often lasts about 45 minutes. In this program, stories of the life of many animals in the world are told in a very lively way. For example, people can watch films about monkeys, snakes, tigers, insects, birds, sea turtles, sharks etc and even the penguins and the polar bears in the far North. While watching these films, I find the everyday life activities and habits of these animals very interesting and full mysteries. In addition, I also learn that it is very important to protect these animals and their living environments because they are part of our valuable natural world. Watching this program makes me very well informed and relaxed after a day of work. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"12\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li value=\"50\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Talk about your favorite sport. </span></span></em></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">These days, people are practicing many types of sport such as swimming, running, cycling, aerobics, tennis, table tennis, badminton, golf and football, etc. My favorite sport is jogging. Jogging is a simple sport to practice because you don&#39;t need any special or expensive equipment like other sports. In fact you just need a good pair of trainers for your self . The most suitable place for jogging is a park or somewhere around a lake near your house. You can also jog on a field or in the forest if you are living in the countryside. For me, I jog for about an hour in the afternoon everyday after work. I usually go jogging alone, but if possible you can ask my family members, friends or neighbors to go with me. While we jog, we often talk and share with each other about everyday life stories, so we feel that we can reduce our stress. After going jogging each day, I feel that I am more relaxed and fit again after a long day of work. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"13\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li value=\"1000\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Talk about one of your close friends. </span></span></em></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\r\n		<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">have had many friends so far, but Thanh Nga is one of my close friends. Nga is about 30 years old and is now working a researcher at an institute in Hanoi. We met each other when we were in the secondary school. During those days, we went to school together everyday, studied in the same class and shared with each other all the joys and sorrow, so we have become close friends since then. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">My friend Nga is not very tall, but pretty with long black hair and a nice smile. She is a very sincere, modest and helpful person. She likes painting and painted many pictures. Also, I can still remember that Nga was very good at literature and foreign languages. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">We often meet each other when we have time. When we are very busy, we often talk to each other on the phone or we chat on the Internet. Whenever we meet, we often go to see other friends, go shopping or sit in a quite place to have coffee. We talk about our life and share with each other our good news or problems and see if we can help each other. Nga is really a good friend of mine, a friend for life. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:88px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"14\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Talk about your house/flat. </span></span></em></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\r\n		<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">live in a house in Hanoi. The house is in a small and quiet street in Cau Giay district of Hanoi. It takes about half an hour to go to the city center. The house was built 5 years ago. It isn&#39;t a big house and has two floors. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In my house there are 4 main rooms: a living room, a dining rooms, two bedrooms. Besides, we have a kitchen, a bathroom and a toilet. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">We have a little but pretty garden; my family often spend our free time there to grow plant and vegetables. Next to the garden there is a small yard where my children often play after school. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1px; text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In my house, I like the living room is my favorite one. This room was painted light green, so we </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">feel very pleasant. In this room, there is a tea table, a sofa and a television. On the wall there is a couple of oil paintings. After dinner, our family often spend time together talking to each other or watching a favorite TV program. We often receive our guests in this room. I love my house. Everyday when I come back home from work, I have a warm feeling of being together with my whole family. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Talk about your job. </span></span></em></span></span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\r\n		<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">am now working as a senior engineer in a company in Hanoi. My company name is ABC Company. I have had this job for more than 10 years. In my job, I am in charge of managing our department&#39;s activities such as research development, technical supervision and maintenance, etc. </span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:41px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Besides, we also need to corporate our work with other departments in the company in order to run the company&#39;s business smoothly. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">To do this job besides my university degree, I have had many training classes in project management, product development, marketing, etc... </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1px; text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In addition, the skills required for this job are communication, time management, teamwork and </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:41px; margin-right:1px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">presentation skills, etc... </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39px; margin-right:1px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">I really like my job because I am able to apply the knowledge and skills of the filed I studied in my work. In addition, I have a flexible working time, so I can make full use of the time in the office and have time for research. Also, I am lucky to work with a very active and supportive staff. One thing I don&#39;t like about this job is that I often have to travel, so I sometimes don&#39;t have time for my family. I am planning to further my study to get a doctor degree. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', 7, 0, '2018-12-24 16:02:49', '2018-12-24 16:02:49', 2, '', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `posts` (`idtin`, `title`, `content`, `user_id`, `is_public`, `createdate`, `updatedate`, `idnhom`, `anhtrichdan`, `videotrichdan`, `noidungtrichdan`) VALUES
(178, 'Luyện nghe bài 2', '<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Hướng dẫn giải đề</strong></span></td>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n</strong></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>C&acirc;u hỏi 01: Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n c&oacute; đại từ nh&acirc;n xưng l&agrave;m chủ ngữ l&agrave; đ&aacute;p &aacute;n sai</strong></span>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Đối với c&aacute;c bức ảnh chỉ c&oacute; sự vật, nếu đại từ nh&acirc;n xưng như he, she, they&hellip; hoặc c&aacute;c từ / cụm từ tương ứng như a man, a woman, people&hellip; được d&ugrave;ng l&agrave;m chủ ngữ trong c&aacute;c đ&aacute;p &aacute;n th&igrave; chắc chắn đ&oacute; l&agrave; những đ&aacute;p &aacute;n sai. Trong trường hợp n&agrave;y, d&ugrave; chỉ mới nghe qua chủ ngũ th&igrave; bạn cũng c&oacute; thể loại trừ được đ&aacute;p &aacute;n sai v&agrave; tập trung t&igrave;m đ&aacute;p &aacute;n đ&uacute;ng trong c&aacute;c c&acirc;u c&ograve;n lại. Ở c&acirc;u hỏi 1, do loại trừ hai đ&aacute;p &aacute;n sai c&oacute; từ he v&agrave; people l&agrave;m chủ ngữ n&ecirc;n ch&uacute;ng ta chỉ cần xem x&eacute;t đ&aacute;p &aacute;n B v&agrave; D. V&igrave; trong bức ảnh c&oacute; 2 chiếc thuyền n&ecirc;n đ&aacute;p &aacute;n D &ndash; với từ boat được d&ugrave;ng ở dạng số nhiều &ndash; l&agrave; đ&aacute;p &aacute;n đ&uacute;ng</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n D</span>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">He&rsquo;s tying the boat to the dock</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">A boat is sailing on the waiter</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">People are swimming in the lake</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Boats are floating on the water</strong></span></li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>C&acirc;u hỏi 02: Ch&uacute; &yacute; về mối quan hệ vị tr&iacute; giữa c&aacute;c sự vật</strong></span>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Nếu trong bức ảnh c&oacute; nhiều sự vật như bức tranh, l&ograve; sưởi, t&uacute;i x&aacute;ch, sopha&hellip; th&igrave; bạn phải ch&uacute; &yacute; đến mối quan hệ về vị tr&iacute; giữa c&aacute;c sự vật. Trong bức ảnh ở c&acirc;u hỏi 2 c&oacute; một b&uacute;c tranh treo tr&ecirc;n l&ograve; sưởi n&ecirc;n đ&aacute;p &aacute;n đ&uacute;ng l&agrave; B. Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n D sai l&agrave; do m&ocirc; tả sai mối quan hệ về vị tr&iacute; giữa sofa v&agrave; television. Nh&igrave;n v&agrave;o bức ảnh, ch&uacute;ng ta thấy sofa kh&ocirc;ng nằm đối diện tivi.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n B</span>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">The living room is being cleaned</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>There is a painting hanging over the fireplace</strong></span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Some potted plants are being watered</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">The sofa is being faced the television</span></li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>C&acirc;u hỏi 03: Chủ ngữ của c&aacute;c đ&aacute;p &aacute;n l&agrave; sự vật v&agrave; đ&ocirc;ng từ được d&ugrave;ng ỏ thể bị động</strong></span>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Ở part 1, nếu c&aacute;c đ&aacute;p &aacute;n c&oacute; chủ ngũ l&agrave; sự vật th&igrave; rất c&oacute; khả năng động từ sẽ được d&ugrave;ng ở thể bị động. Ở cấu tr&uacute;c n&agrave;y, động từ be được đọc nối &acirc;m n&ecirc;n bạn sẽ kh&oacute; nhận biết. Mặt kh&aacute;c, c&oacute; thể bạn cũng khonog nghe kịp c&aacute;c cụm từ being packed , being unloaded (khi động từ pack v&agrave; unload được d&ugrave;ng ở thể bị động của th&igrave; hiện tại tiếp diễn). Bức ảnh ở c&acirc;u hỏi 3 cho thấy c&aacute;c th&ugrave;ng giấy đang được xếp chồng l&ecirc;n nhau n&ecirc;n đ&aacute;p &aacute;n đ&uacute;ng l&agrave; D. H&atilde;y ghi nhớ cụm từ be stacked up, đ&acirc;y l&agrave; cụm từ thường được sử dụng trong bức ảnh c&oacute; nhiều đồ vật xếp chồng l&ecirc;n nhau.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n D</span>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Items are being packed into containers</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">They&rsquo;re carrying boxed through the door</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Several crates are being unloaded from a truck</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>The boxes are being stacked up on top of each other</strong></span></li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>C&acirc;u hỏi 04: Thể bị động của th&igrave; hiện tại tiếp diễn v&agrave; thể bị động của th&igrave; hiện tại ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh</strong></span>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Trong nhiều trường hợp, chủ ngữ của c&aacute;c đ&aacute;p &aacute;n đ&uacute;ng l&agrave; sự vật v&agrave; động từ được d&ugrave;ng ở thể bị động của th&igrave; hiện tại tiếp diễn (is/are+being+pp) hoặc thể bị động của th&igrave; hiện tại ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh (have/has+been+pp). Đối với bức ảnh chỉ c&oacute; đồ vật th&igrave; rất c&oacute; thể những đ&aacute;p &aacute;n sử đụng thể bị động của th&igrave; hiện tại tiếp diễn l&agrave; đ&aacute;p &aacute;n sai, v&igrave; cấu tr&uacute;c n&agrave;y gắn liền với chủ thể đang thực hiện h&agrave;nh động. Ở c&acirc;u hỏi 4, bức ảnh cho thấy đĩa đ&atilde; được b&agrave;y sẵn tr&ecirc;n b&agrave;n n&ecirc;n A l&agrave; đ&aacute;p &aacute;n đ&uacute;ng. Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n D sai v&igrave; sử dụng thể bị động của th&igrave; hiện tại tiếp diễn trong khi kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; người n&agrave;o đang đặt thức ăn l&ecirc;n b&agrave;n.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n A</span>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Some plates have been places on the table</strong></span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">The glasses are filled with wine</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Cups are being washed in the sink</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Food is being served at the table</span></li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>C&acirc;u hỏi 05: Cấu tr&uacute;c c&acirc;u there is&hellip;/There are&hellip; được d&ugrave;ng để m&ocirc; tả vị tr&iacute; của sự vật</strong></span>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Đối với c&aacute;c bức ảnh chỉ c&oacute; sự vật th&igrave; trong số c&aacute;c đ&aacute;p &aacute;n bạn nghe được thường c&oacute; 1 số đ&aacute;p &aacute;n sử dụng cấu tr&uacute;c c&acirc;u there is&hellip;/There are&hellip; để m&ocirc; tả vị tr&iacute; của sự vật. Lưu &yacute; c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;t &acirc;m của cụm từ There are&hellip; v&igrave; bạn c&oacute; thể nghe nhầm th&agrave;nh they&rsquo;re (chủ ngữ chỉ người)</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n D</span>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<ol>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">People are entering the church</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">The building is being constructed</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">A field stretches to the river</span></li>\r\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>There are clouds in the sky</strong></span></li>\r\n			</ol>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 7, 0, '2019-01-01 16:27:54', '2019-01-01 16:27:54', 3, '', 'video/part1-dang3.mp4', '<h2><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Giới thiệu về c&acirc;u hỏi :</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Khung cảnh trong bức ảnh c&oacute; thể l&agrave; cảnh trong nh&agrave; (văn ph&ograve;ng, cửa h&agrave;ng, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng&hellip;) hoặc cảnh ngo&agrave;i trời (đường phố, bờ biển, c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Trong nhiều trường hợp, bạn cần x&aacute;c định xem đ&aacute;p &aacute;n c&oacute; m&ocirc; tả đ&uacute;ng mối quan hệ về vị tr&iacute; giữa c&aacute;c sự vật hay kh&ocirc;ng</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Động từ trong c&aacute;c đ&aacute;p &aacute;n chủ yếu được dung ở thể bị động (th&igrave; hiện tại tiếp diễn hoặc hiện tại ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Dạng c&acirc;u hỏi n&agrave;y thường c&oacute; đ&aacute;p &aacute;n sai l&agrave; đ&aacute;p &aacute;n m&ocirc; tả con người</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Đ&aacute;p &aacute;n đề cập đến sự vật trong bức ảnh cũng c&oacute; thể l&agrave; đ&aacute;p &aacute;n sai</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
(148, ' Audio chủ đề Accident', '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">I wonder how many accidents I&rsquo;ve had in my life. I&rsquo;ve had a few serious ones where I&rsquo;ve ended up in hospital. Traffic accidents are the worst. They&rsquo;re always painful. I haven&rsquo;t had too many work-related accidents. I suppose that&rsquo;s because I do office work and that&rsquo;s not so dangerous. Most of my accidents are those around the house. I&rsquo;ve lost count of the number of times I&rsquo;ve hit my thumb with a hammer. I&rsquo;m also really good at standing up and hitting my head on something. I&rsquo;m not as bad as my friend though. He&rsquo;s a real accident looking for somewhere to happen. Almost every time we meet, he has some story to tell about his latest accident. He&rsquo;s quite unbelievable. I think I&rsquo;d be very worried if I were his mother.</span></span></p>\r\n', 7, 0, '2018-12-30 17:36:10', '2018-12-30 17:36:10', 3, 'audio/accidents.mp3', '', '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Try the online &nbsp;listening, and activities on grammar, spelling and vocabulary for this lesson on&nbsp;<strong>Accidents.</strong></span></span></p>\r\n'),
(150, 'Audio chủ đề education', '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">I wonder how many accidents I&rsquo;ve had in my life. I&rsquo;ve had a few serious ones where I&rsquo;ve ended up in hospital. Traffic accidents are the worst. They&rsquo;re always painful. I haven&rsquo;t had too many work-related accidents. I suppose that&rsquo;s because I do office work and that&rsquo;s not so dangerous. Most of my accidents are those around the house. I&rsquo;ve lost count of the number of times I&rsquo;ve hit my thumb with a hammer. I&rsquo;m also really good at standing up and hitting my head on something. I&rsquo;m not as bad as my friend though. He&rsquo;s a real accident looking for somewhere to happen. Almost every time we meet, he has some story to tell about his latest accident. He&rsquo;s quite unbelievable. I think I&rsquo;d be very worried if I were his mother.</span></span></p>\r\n', 7, 0, '2018-12-31 16:04:52', '2018-12-31 16:04:52', 3, 'audio/education.mp3', '', '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Try the online&nbsp; listening, and activities on grammar, spelling and vocabulary for this lesson on&nbsp;<strong>Accidents</strong>.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n'),
(151, 'Audio chủ đề Information', '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">We are living in an age of information. That&rsquo;s what I keep hearing on TV and reading in newspapers. We are surrounded by information technology that puts information at our fingertips. To get ahead, you need the latest information. I&rsquo;m not really sure how much information we need. Our brains can only handle a certain amount of information at a time. I reckon a lot of us have information overload. I&rsquo;m sure before computers came along this didn&rsquo;t happen. One problem with computers is the amount of personal information online. I worry about putting confidential info on different websites. Of course the great thing about computers is that we have so much information at our disposal. That&rsquo;s pretty useful.</span></span></p>\r\n', 7, 0, '2018-12-31 16:27:48', '2018-12-31 16:27:48', 3, 'audio/information.mp3', '', '<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Try the online quiz, reading, listening, and activities on grammar, spelling and vocabulary for this lesson on&nbsp;<strong>Information</strong>.</span></span></p>\r\n');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`idtin`, `title`, `content`, `user_id`, `is_public`, `createdate`, `updatedate`, `idnhom`, `anhtrichdan`, `videotrichdan`, `noidungtrichdan`) VALUES
(153, 'Danh sách từ vựng UNIT 1,2', '<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">UNIT 1 </span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"TableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:solid black 1.0pt; margin-left:40px; width:548.85pt\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#404040; border-color:black; height:25.9pt; width:202.25pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:white\">WORDS </span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#404040; border-color:black; height:25.9pt; width:90.0pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:white\">PRONOUNCE </span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#404040; border-color:black; height:25.9pt; width:256.55pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:white\">MEANING </span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black; height:26.8pt; vertical-align:top; width:202.25pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Things you do with friends </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:26.8pt; vertical-align:top; width:90.0pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:26.8pt; vertical-align:top; width:256.55pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Những điều bạn l&agrave;m với bạn của bạn </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black; height:24.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:202.25pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:31px\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Borrow (a CD from someone) </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:24.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:90.0pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:24.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:256.55pt\">\r\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Mượn (một chiếc đĩa CD từ ai đ&oacute;) </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black; height:24.25pt; vertical-align:top; width:202.25pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:31