te\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">30</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>A</strong>&nbsp; or&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>B</strong>&nbsp; if&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>C</strong>&nbsp; but</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">31</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>A</strong>&nbsp; them&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>B</strong>&nbsp; him&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>C</strong>&nbsp; us</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">32</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>A</strong>&nbsp; from&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>B</strong>&nbsp; by&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>C</strong>&nbsp; to</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">33</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>A</strong>&nbsp; the&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>B</strong>&nbsp; a&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>C</strong>&nbsp; any</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:27px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f8f8f8\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">PART III. WRITING </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><em><span style=\"background-color:#f8f8f8\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Task 1. Arrange the given words into a complete sentence</span></span></em></strong></span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f0f3f5\"><em><span style=\"color:#333333\">1, Late/ working/&nbsp; suggests/ tonight / she</span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f0f3f5\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">-&gt;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f0f3f5\"><em><span style=\"color:#333333\">2. promise/ I/ pass/ the/ harder/ to/ exam/ next/ to/ study</span></em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f0f3f5\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">-&gt;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f0f3f5\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">3. with/ her/ lives/ Hoa/ in/ uncle/ aunt/ Ha Noi/ and.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f0f3f5\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">-&gt;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f0f3f5\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">4. I/ a lot of/ when/ do/ can/ what/ have/ I/ money ?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f0f3f5\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">-&gt;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f0f3f5\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">5. boyfriend/ going/ I/ out/ with/ my/ can&rsquo;t</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f0f3f5\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">-&gt;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:27px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:27px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Task2: </strong><br />\r\n<strong>Write a note/email of about 35-45 words about your last holiday/trip</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Where you went</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">What you did</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">What you liked best about your hoiday/trip</span></span></span></p>\r\n', 7, 0, '2019-01-01 10:00:30', '2019-01-01 10:00:30', 9, '', '', '');
