nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color:black\">B. I don&rsquo;t know</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; C. I will</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">14. Margaret &ldquo;Could you open the window, please&rdquo;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Henry &ldquo;_______&rdquo;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">A. I feel sorry&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; B I am, of course&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; C. Yes, with pleasure&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">15. Bob: &ldquo;I would like to try on these shoes, please&rdquo; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Salgirl: &ldquo;_____&rdquo;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Why not&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;B. By all mean, sir&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs